---
// AuthModal.astro
---
<section id="auth-overlay" class="auth-overlay">
	<div class="auth-card" id="auth-card">
		<div class="auth-header">
			<img src="https://hosted.inled.es/bitid-animated.gif" alt="BitID Logo" class="apple-id-logo" />
			<h1 id="auth-title">BitID</h1>
		</div>
		
		<div id="auth-unlock-view" class="auth-view hidden">
			<p class="auth-subtitle">Inicia sesión con tu BitID para acceder a BitMeet.</p>
			<div class="apple-input-wrapper">
				<input type="password" id="master-password" placeholder="Contraseña Maestra" autofocus />
				<button id="btn-unlock-app" class="arrow-submit-btn">
					<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
				</button>
			</div>
			<div style="margin-top: 16px;">
				<a href="#" style="color: #0066cc; text-decoration: none; font-size: 14px;">¿Olvidaste la contraseña?</a>
			</div>
		</div>
		
		<div id="auth-import-view" class="auth-view hidden">
			<p class="auth-subtitle">Bienvenido! No hemos encontrado tu passkey en la memoria de tu dispositivo. Impórtala o sincronízala con otro dispositivo.</p>
			
			<div class="auth-import-actions">
				<button id="btn-trigger-import" class="apple-button-primary">Importar BitID (.json)</button>
				<input type="file" id="import-file" class="hidden" accept=".json" />
				
				<div class="auth-divider">o mediante código</div>
				
				<div class="sync-input-group">
					<input type="text" id="pairing-code-input" placeholder="Código de 6 dígitos" maxlength="6" />
					<button id="btn-sync-by-code" class="apple-button-arrow">
						<svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.5"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg>
					</button>
				</div>
			</div>

			<p style="margin-top: 32px; font-size: 12px; color: #86868b;">Si no tienes un ID, créalo en <a href="https://id.inled.es" target="_blank" style="color: #0066cc; text-decoration: none;">id.inled.es</a></p>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>

<style>
	.auth-import-actions {
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 16px;
		margin-top: 24px;
	}

	.auth-divider {
		text-align: center;
		position: relative;
		font-size: 13px;
		color: #86868b;
		margin: 8px 0;
	}

	.auth-divider::before,
	.auth-divider::after {
		content: "";
		position: absolute;
		top: 50%;
		width: 30%;
		height: 1px;
		background: #d2d2d7;
	}

	.auth-divider::before { left: 0; }
	.auth-divider::after { right: 0; }

	.sync-input-group {
		position: relative;
		width: 100%;
	}

	.sync-input-group input {
		width: 100% !important;
		padding: 14px 44px 14px 16px !important;
		border-radius: 12px !important;
		border: 1px solid #d2d2d7 !important;
		font-size: 17px !important;
		background: #fff !important;
		color: #1d1d1f !important;
		outline: none !important;
		text-align: center;
		letter-spacing: 2px;
		font-weight: 600;
	}

	.sync-input-group input:focus {
		border-color: #0071e3 !important;
		box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(0, 113, 227, 0.1) !important;
	}

	.apple-button-arrow {
		position: absolute;
		right: 8px;
		top: 50%;
		transform: translateY(-50%);
		background: #0071e3;
		color: white;
		border: none;
		width: 30px;
		height: 30px;
		border-radius: 50%;
		cursor: pointer;
		display: flex;
		align-items: center;
		justify-content: center;
		padding: 0;
		transition: transform 0.2s, background 0.2s;
	}

	.apple-button-arrow:hover {
		background: #0077ed;
		transform: translateY(-50%) scale(1.05);
	}
</style>
